name: Lionage - iPhone 5 Case
description:
Each 3RDi iPhone 5 case is made of a durable plastic hardshell construction. These cases are specifically designed to shelter your Apple iPhone® 5 from dust and scratches while providing an aesthetically beautiful look. There is no need to remove the case to utilize the iPhone’s features; Its unique design allows access to all iPhone accessory ports, the dock connector, lock button, volume button, and camera lens/flash. The installation process is quick and simple. The thin, low profile structure is a stylish way to keep your iPhone's surface free of scratches and scuffs all the while looking great.
Features:


	•	Low profile design showcases more of your iPhone 5
	•	Precise cutouts give full access to all ports 
	•	Compatible with Apple iPhone 5

name: Truth Serum - iPhone 4/4S Case
description:
Each 3RDi iPhone case is made of a durable rubber hardshell construction, which resembles hard plastic, but is flexible and soft to the touch. It provides an anti-slip grip with a soft, more comfortable feeling. 3RDi’s cases are specifically designed to shelter your Apple iPhone® 4/4S from dust, scratches, and shock! It’s raised wrap around edges helps protect the glass screen from damage when placed face down.  There is no need to remove the case to utilize the iPhone’s features; Its unique design allows access to all iPhone accessory ports, the dock connector, lock button, volume button, and camera lens/flash. The installation process is quick and simple. The thin, yet durable structure is a stylish way to keep your iPhone's surface free of scratches and scuffs.
Features:


	•	Easy-to-grip, soft yet durable material
	•	Raised wrap around edges helps protect glass screen from damage when placed face down
	•	Shock absorbent and shatterproof
	•	Precise cutouts give full access to all ports 
	•	Compatible with Apple iPhone 4 & 4S
